original_title: NPP wins Monaragala, Mihintale, Kundasale and Medawachchiya
original_body_lines: National People’s Power (NPP) has also won in the Mihintale polling division in Anuradhapura District, Kundasale polling division in Kandy District, Monaragala polling division in Monaragala District and Medawachchiya polling division in Anuradhapura District.
